column3: Collecting a fledgling, are we? I'll need to see the proof of covering...
Well, well! I see someone is ready to run! Here's your fledgling's registration form─the rest I leave to you.
What's that? No proof of covering? <sigh> What did I just say?
To collect your newborn fledgling, you must present the proof of covering to Katering.
Someone's awfully eager─too eager, that is. These things take time, in case you've forgotten.
You cannot collect your fledgling prior to the date specified on your proof of covering.
